{"tid":1813622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港新任市長倡每日工作24小時","createTime":"2020-01-06T11:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T15:41:50.000Z","uid":57073,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a4db0a92e0f2bd6c299549b7a4cd3afaba8a9316","tid":1813622,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"外電Nineup報專訊報道，62歲香港市新任女市長林鄭柒鵝(Seven Lam Cheng)建議實施彈性工作制，每周工作7天及每天工作24小時，讓中國香港人民有更多時間為港貢獻，並培養愛好、享受工作的其他方面。<br />\n<br />\n柒鵝強調，讓香港二等公民維持工作量很重要，是向1200選委提供幫助和信守承諾。提議出台後，立即受到香港市聯盟、勞福局祕書支持。<br />\n<br />\n香港市目前實行常規工作制，即每周工作6天，每天工作12小時。而在祖國中國，自2020年以來已開始實施每天16小時工作制，結果顯示，員工更快樂，工作效率更高。<br />\n<br />\n曰本微硬公司去年也推行新工作制度試驗，將每年休息日增至3天，結果生產率驚人地上升399％。<br />\n<br />\n柒鵝生於1957年5月，2020年就職，是香港市第一位市長，同時也是全香港市最年輕的政府領導人之一。"},{"pid":"90c63578466d2e7c786cc412e6a665e7c91d85df","tid":1813622,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:54:13.000Z","msg":"每日工作24小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af2e99444b1e2a60e38ab71cc1b80d47decbe98","tid":1813622,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c229d28cc93537f62c667e7891b21dffd1b39cdc","tid":1813622,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6367385d5e39d26d3f0ed5f56fbf388750975dd3","tid":1813622,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a236a0285aeb751bc07691babd82813813d6d123","tid":1813622,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:06:07.000Z","msg":"納dee?"},{"pid":"366e63336203a17d754daba501aae53ffc2863fd","tid":1813622,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img 